---
import Logo from '../ui/Logo.astro';

const navLinks = [
    { href: '#problemy', label: 'Diagnoza' },
    { href: '#oferta', label: 'Oferta' },
    { href: '#dowod', label: 'Rezultaty' },
    { href: '#proces', label: 'Proces' },
];
---
<footer class="bg-background-muted border-t border-slate-200/80">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
            <div class="md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
                <Logo width={200} />
                <p class="mt-4 text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Zarządzanie medycyną zredukowane do perfekcji. Podnosimy efektywność i bezpieczeństwo prawne placówek medycznych.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary tracking-wider uppercase">Mapa Strony</h4>
                <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
                    {navLinks.map(link => (
                        <li>
                            <a href={link.href} class="text-base text-text-muted hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">
                                {link.label}
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    ))}
                    <li>
                        <a href="#kontakt" class="text-base text-text-muted hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">
                            Kontakt
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary tracking-wider uppercase">Kontakt</h4>
                <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
                    <li>
                        <a href="tel:+48123456789" class="text-base text-text-muted hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">
                            +48 123 456 789
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="mailto:kontakt@koordynujzdrowie.pl" class="text-base text-text-muted hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">
                            kontakt@koordynujzdrowie.pl
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-base text-text-muted">
                        Warszawa, Polska
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary tracking-wider uppercase">Social Media</h4>
                <div class="flex space-x-4 mt-4">
                    <a href="#" class="text-text-muted hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">
                        <span class="sr-only">LinkedIn</span>
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">
                &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Koordynuj Zdrowie. Wszelkie prawa zastrzeżone.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>